Class MyPriorityQueue<T>

java.lang.Object
MyPriorityQueue<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of elements stored in the priority queue
All Implemented Interfaces:
PriorityQueueADT<T>
public class MyPriorityQueue<T> extends Object implements PriorityQueueADT<T>
Generic priority queue implementation. Elements are stored in priority order as determined by the provided Comparator. The default capacity is 10, and the maximum capacity is 1000.
